OL,3,C'Pints' of wine to be stocked in
OL,4,CBritish supermarkets for first time
OL,6,F"Pint" sized bottles of still and
OL,7,Fsparkling wine, in the form of a new
OL,8,F568ml amount, are soon to appear on
OL,9,Fsupermarket shelves and in pubs, clubs
OL,10,Fand restaurants, the government has
OL,11,Fannounced.
OL,13,FThe move to introduce the 568ml size
OL,14,Fwill sit alongside 200ml and 500ml
OL,15,Fmeasures already available, offering
OL,16,Fmore flexibility and choice for
OL,17,Fcustomers, the Department for Business
OL,18,Fand Trade said.
